name: Franklin Global Growth Fund
longDescription: In pursuing its investment objective, the underlying fund employs a bottom-up investment approach and follows a growth investment style in selecting investments for the underlying funds portfolio; may invest up to 20 percent of its assets in equity securities of issuers in emerging markets. Franklin Global Growth Active ETF seeks to provide longterm capital appreciation through exposure to equity securities of growth companies with any market size capitalization, located anywhere in the world, by investing substantially all of its assets in securities of Franklin Global Growth Fund.
